OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry but breezy, with cloud
OL,7,Fmoving inland overnight then burning
OL,8,Fback to the coast by day to give sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Temperatures above average for
OL,10,Fmost, cooler along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
